Description:
    Provides wrappers for the julia package 'gswdesign', which is a computationally
    efficient implementation of the Gram-Schmidt walk design.
    See <https://github.com/fsavje/gswdesign-R> for more information.
SystemRequirements: Julia (>= 1.0.5), Random.jl, LinearAlgebra.jl
